arnath ||\n|-\n| ''[[Vanaja Girija]]'' || ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"10\"| 1995 || ''[[Engirundho Vandhan]]'' || Sundaram's son ||\n|-\n| ''[[Kattumarakaran]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Lucky Man (film)|Lucky Man]]'' || Gopikrishna's friend ||\n|-\n| ''[[Avatharam (1995 film)|Avatharam]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Thedi Vandha Raasa]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Mayabazar (1995 film)|Mayabazaar]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Pongalo Pongal]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Raasaiyya]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Mr. Madras]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Seethanam]]'' || ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\"| 1996 || ''[[Thayagam]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Irattai Roja]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Enakkoru Magan Pirappan]]'' || Vargis ||\n|-\n| ''[[Andha Naal (1996 film)|Andha Naal]]'' || Kandu ||\n|-\n| ''[[Senathipathi]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Purushan Pondatti]]'' || ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\"| 1997 || ''[[Paththini (1997 film)|Paththini]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Dhinamum Ennai Gavani]]'' || Ganesan ||\n|-\n| ''[[Sishya (film)|Sishya]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Pongalo Pongal]]'' || Anja Nenjam ||\n|-\n| ''[[Paththini (1997 film)|Paththini]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Arasiyal]]'' || Thiruvasagam ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\"| 1998 || ''[[Color Kanavugal]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Harichandra (1998 film)|Harichandra]]'' || General Manager ||\n|-\n| ''[[Golmaal (1998 film)|Golmaal]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[En Uyir Nee Thaane]]'' || Police inspector ||\n|-\n| ''[[Kumbakonam Gopalu]]'' || ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 1999 || ''[[Chinna Durai (1999 film)|Chinna Durai]]'' || ||\n|-\n|''[[Viralukketha Veekkam]]'' || Karuppaiyya ||\n|-\n| ''[[Sangamam]]'' || ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\"| 2000 || ''[[Kadhal Rojavae]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Vallarasu]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Sandhitha Velai]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Koodi Vazhnthal Kodi Nanmai (2000 film)|Koodi Vazhnthal Kodi Nanmai]]'' || Veerapandi ||\n|-\n| ''[[Simmasanam]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Kuberan (2000 film)|Kuberan]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Seenu (2000 film)|Seenu]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Vanna Thamizh Pattu]]'' || Ponnusamy ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\"| 2001 || ''[[Vaanchinathan]]'' || Naraya